reviewText: What I've been able to watch of the show it's been good but the quality of the DVDs are poor.  Season 1 skipped so much I missed several episodes.  Decided to move on to season 2 which is no better.  This time the DVD froze.  At first I thought it was my equipment but I'm happy to say it is not.  The DVDs are at fault.  Maybe one day these shows will be Netflex.
Seems really nice.  Need more time to evalute better.
